msdyn_trainingconfigschema:
[
  {
    "name": "numberOfGlobalPredictors",
    "displayName": "Number of Global predictors",
    "description": "Defines the number of global predictors to be output during training",
    "defaultValue": "10",
    "type": "Edm.Int32"
  },
  {
    "name": "chiSqCorrelationThresholdForTargetLeak",
    "displayName": "Threshold for Target leak using Chi Square Coeff",
    "description": "Defines the threshold for target leak using Chi Square correlation coefficient during training",
    "defaultValue": "0.9",
    "type": "Edm.Double"
  },
  {
    "name": "personCorrelationThresholdForTargetLeak",
    "displayName": "Threshold for Target leak using Pearson Coeff",
    "description": "Defines the threshold for target leak using Pearson correlation coefficient during training",
    "defaultValue": "0.9",
    "type": "Edm.Double"
  },
  {
    "name": "maxThresholdForOneHotEncoding",
    "displayName": "Threshold for distinct values for one hot encoding",
    "description": "Defines the threshold for distinct values for one hot encoding during training",
    "defaultValue": "20",
    "type": "Edm.Int32"
  },
  {
    "name": "isCustomPipelinesEnabled",
    "displayName": "Is Custom Pipelines enabled for run",
    "description": "Defines if the AI Config is enabled for Custom Pipelines",
    "defaultValue": "True",
    "type": "Edm.Boolean"
  },
  {
    "name": "customPipelineYaml",
    "displayName": "Custom Pipeline Yaml",
    "description": "Defines the yaml file to be used for training",
    "defaultValue": "GP-Train-Pipeline.yaml",
    "type": "Edm.String"
  }
]
